highlights.text: “Poovukkul Olindhirukkum - Jeans” by Roshan Sebastian and Kevin Jason is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kochi, up 49 spots at #38.
“Vaathil Melle” by Rajesh Murugesan and Sachin Warrier is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kochi at #47.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Kochi. “Thenmozhi (From "Thiruchitrambalam")” is the highest at #6.
“Munbe Vaa” by A.R. Rahman, Shreya Ghoshal, and Naresh Iyer has been on Top Songs Kochi the longest, at 67 weeks straight.
